      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "InProgress复合状态已完成，包含Started→InReview子流程，以及到OnHold和Cancelled的退出路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "InProgress",
        "Started",
        "InReview",
