      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Blocked和Deferred的恢复路径不一样吧？Blocked应该是Unblock回到POS系统，Deferred是Prioritize回到库存？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Blocked",
